{"lemma":"أَغْلَف","slug":"أَغْلَف","root":"غ.ل.ف","root_slug":"غ-ل-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ل-ف","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n32278"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%BA%D9%92%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%81"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"uncircumcised"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"uncivilized, impolite, rude"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Color or defect adjective from the root غ ل ف (ḡ l f)."},"ipa":["/ʔaɣ.laf/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n32278","headword_ar":"اَغْلَفُ","root":"glf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Enclosed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gilaAf","text_ar":"غِلَاف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]; applied in this sense to a sword, as also [the fem.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galofaA='u","text_ar":"غَلْفَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to a bow; (S, O, K;) and likewise to anything. (S, O. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mugal~afN","text_ar":"مُغَلَّفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b2-  And A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having upon him a sort of garment from beneath which he has not put forth his fore arms."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Khálid Ibn-Jembeh, L, TA.) ―         -b3-  And, applied to a man,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqolafu","text_ar":"اَقْلَفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Mgh, O, K;) i. e. (Mgh)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Uncircumcised:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb:) fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galofaA='u","text_ar":"غَلْفَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baZorN","text_ar":"بَظْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gulofN","text_ar":"غُلْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) ―         -b4-  Applied also to a heart, meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"As thought it were covered with a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gilaAf","text_ar":"غِلَاف"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that it does not learn;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K, TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covered from hearing and accepting the truth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gilaAfN","text_ar":"غِلَافٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". [And see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mugal~afN","text_ar":"مُغَلَّفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN galofaA='u","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ غَلْفَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A land that has not been depastured, so that there is in it every sort of small and large herbage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, O, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sanapN galofaA='u","text_ar":"سَنَةٌ غَلْفَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A year in which is abundance of herbage;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA;) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmN A^agolafu","text_ar":"عَامٌ اَغْلَفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eayo$N","text_ar":"عَيْشٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agolafu","text_ar":"اَغْلَفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Life that is ample in its means"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"circumstances, unstraitened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plentiful, and easy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}